    <h1 class="text-center mt-2">Not For Consumption</h1>
    <hr class="rule" />

    <p>
      Every product sold by Perni Cious Remedies is a <strong>decorative item</strong>.
      Bottles ship empty. Labels are satirical fiction.
      Nothing offered here is a food, a beverage, a dietary supplement,
      a drug, a cosmetic, a medical device, or a remedy in the medical sense.
    </p>

    <p>
      No claim made on any label, packaging, product description, social media post,
      or printed material should be understood as literal, scientific, medical, or serious.
      Anything resembling a medical claim is parody and is protected as satirical expression.
    </p>

    <p>
      Do not ingest, inhale, apply to skin, administer to animals, rely upon for medical
      decision-making, or present in a court of law any item sold by Perni Cious Remedies.
      Keep out of reach of children who might be confused by our aesthetic commitment.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you require real medical advice, please consult a licensed physician.
      If you require real therapy, please consult a licensed therapist.
      If you require real courage, we regret to inform you it cannot, in fact,
      be bottled.
    </p>

    <p class="eyebrow text-center mt-12">— The Management</p>
  </article>
